snippet.title: Cae Valentine
snippet.description:
Here ill be tackling issues like feminism and social justice and other subjects i find stupid.


Avi used is by piper steed aka @fyzzgiggidy on twitter, check her out and commission some work from her, shes a fabulous artist.

Support my patreon here: https://www.patreon.com/caev all pledges will go towards better equipment.
